# Steer a TCP flow onto provider wanA by stamping its fwmark (0x1) in prerouting, ahead of the
# routing decision (ADR-0042). The provider's ip-rule (providers file) then selects wanA's table.
# Only the matched dport is marked; any other flow is left unmarked and follows the default route.
#ACTION      SOURCE   DEST   PROTO   DPORT
MARK(0x1)    loc      -      tcp     9238
